from the top perspective, FloodMonitoring is made of Gateway, Sensor1, Sensor2, Sensor3, Sensor4, 
StimuliGenerator1, StimuliGenerator2, StimuliGenerator3, StimuliGenerator4, and JMonkeyInt! 

from the top perspective, StimuliGenerator1 sends Data to Sensor1!
from the top perspective, Sensor1 sends DataRequest to StimuliGenerator1!
from the top perspective, StimuliGenerator2 sends Data to Sensor2!
from the top perspective, Sensor2 sends DataRequest to StimuliGenerator2!
from the top perspective, StimuliGenerator3 sends Data to Sensor3!
from the top perspective, Sensor3 sends DataRequest to StimuliGenerator3!
from the top perspective, StimuliGenerator4 sends Data to Sensor4!
from the top perspective, Sensor4 sends DataRequest to StimuliGenerator4!

from the top perspective, Sensor4 sends Data to Sensor3!
from the top perspective, Sensor3 sends Data to Sensor2!
from the top perspective, Sensor2 sends Data to Sensor1!
from the top perspective, Sensor1 sends Data to Gateway!

from the top perspective, Gateway sends Alert to FloodMonitoring!